# dmtoolkit

!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! NOT YET STABLE !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

![Tests](https://github.com/Sallenmoore/autonomous/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg)

- **[pypi](https://pypi.org/project/dmtoolkit/)**
- **[github](https://github.com/Sallenmoore/dmtoolkit)**

## Setup

Add the following to your .env file:

```bash
#### OpenAI Config
OPENAI_KEY=

### Cloudinary Config
CLOUD_NAME=
CLOUDINARY_KEY=
CLOUDINARY_SECRET=

### WikiJS Config

WIKIJS_TOKEN = ""
WIKIJS_URL = ""

# DEV OPTIONS

DEBUG=True
TESTING=True
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
```

